Splishy Fish is so hungry! Help him gobble his fish food as he travels through the aquarium. But watch out for the rocks, they’ll stop him in his tracks!

Game Instructions
Tap or click to play.

Tap Splishy Fish to start. Continuously tap the fish to keep him from falling. Adjust your tapping speed to guide Splishy Fish through the aquarium to gobble up fish food to earn points. Don’t let him fall OR hit the rocks!

Good luck!
